### Unified Players Endpoint Tests
### This endpoint now handles both all players and paginated requests

### 1. Get All Players (no parameters)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 2. Get All Players (explicitly no parameters)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 3. Get Paginated Players (page 0, size 5)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 4. Get Paginated Players (page 1, size 5)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?page=1&size=5
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 5. Get Paginated Players (only page parameter - uses default size 10)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?page=0
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 6. Get Paginated Players (only size parameter - uses default page 0)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?size=3
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 7. Get Paginated Players with Sorting (by firstName, descending)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?page=0&size=5&sortBy=firstName&sortDirection=desc
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 8. Get Paginated Players with Sorting (by lastName, ascending)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?page=0&size=5&sortBy=lastName&sortDirection=asc
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### 9. Test without authentication (should return 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?page=0&size=5

###

### 10. Test with wrong authentication (should return 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/players/paginated?page=0&size=5
Authorization: Basic d3Jvbmc6d3Jvbmc=

### 